reviewText: Very boring movie, would not buy again!  However, the condition was as described by seller and arrived as expected.
Quick shipping!! Perfect gift for my daughter!
Love Hotel For Dogs.  Watched this movie with my granddaughter many times for many years.  Lost my copy and had to have another one.
Hotel for dogs. The five stars is for Hotel for Dogs.  This is a fantastic family movie. Best in show....we didn't care for it. I'd give it a three stars.
This was a big hit as a Christmas present.
Love both these movies, but especially Hotel For Dogs. We watch it a lot and it just keeps getting better. It is a modern day classic.
